🏥 Healthcare Analytics Report (2020–2025)
📌 Project Overview

The Healthcare Analytics Report is a Power BI dashboard built using a synthetic hospital dataset containing 9,742 patient records from 2020 to 2025.

The report is divided into two main analytical sections:

Patient Demographics

Clinical Insights

The dashboard provides interactive, KPI-driven insights into patient distribution, admission patterns, medical conditions, billing analysis, medication usage, doctor performance, and overall hospital operations.

This report supports data-driven decision-making for hospital administrators and healthcare analysts.

📂 Dataset Summary

The dataset consists of:

9,742 patients

14 structured attributes

20 doctors

6 medical conditions

4 admission types

8 medications

3 test result categories

Billing calculated based on disease & hospital stay duration

Admission period: 2020–2025

The dataset was cleaned and validated using Microsoft Excel, then modeled in Power BI with relationships and DAX measures.

